author: Bianca Giulione
title: Nicki Minaj Just Signed With Wilhelmina Models
text:
Nicki Minaj just officially added another profession to her already extensive list – model. According to Vogue , she just signed with illustrious modelling agency Wilhelmina Models, joining their celebrity division. It’s a natural move for the American rap superstar who’s no stranger to striking a pose; whether it’s on the red carpet, for her 77 million Instagram followers, or in campaigns for designers like Roberto Cavalli. 
Oh yea. That too. 🙏🏽🦄💕🎀😛 thank you #Vogue for breaking this story. Honored to be @wilhelminamodels 
A post shared by Nicki Minaj (@nickiminaj) on Mar 28, 2017 at 5:02pm PDT 

Nicki had this to say about her new endeavour: “I love the synergy between my music and how it inspires my fashion. My message is always celebrating your own style… I’m thrilled and honored to have signed with Wilhelmina—they get me.” 
As of late, Nicki is still releasing bangers, recently releasing 3 tracks featuring Lil Wayne and Drake. The Remy Ma-clapback “No Frauds” is a particularly excellent gem, and it was selected as one of our Best Tracks of the Week . 
Revisit “No Frauds” below.

In other music news, Lana Del Rey and The Weeknd have worked on a new track together. Get all the details right here .
